          <p class="list-group-item-text">10.1.5 use a bike for any business purposes;</p>

          <p class="list-group-item-text">10.1.6 load the bike with a total weight of more than 120 kilograms;</p>

          <p class="list-group-item-text">10.1.7 carry any illegal or dangerous objects;</p>

          <p class="list-group-item-text">10.1.8 use the bike in a reckless or dangerous manner and you must not use the
